 CIFAR100 datasets, where\nextensive comparisons, analyses, and insights are provided. To our best\nknowledge, this is the first work that studies SNN compression in a\ncomprehensive manner by exploiting all compressible components and achieves\nbetter results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 3 Nov 2019 04:07:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Jul 2020 01:22:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 20 Aug 2020 06:42:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-21"}
