ficient on-line implementation (less than 1 second) and provide high\nprobability of thermal comfort under uncertainties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 3 Nov 2019 06:17:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Jul 2020 06:24:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 4 Feb 2021 05:05:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-05"}
